<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gab's Scrapbook</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&family=Homemade+Apple&family=Special+Elite&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #e6dfcf;
            --ink: #2b2621;
            --sage-tape: rgba(135, 169, 130, 0.4);
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/papyrus.png');
            color: var(--ink);
            font-family: 'Special Elite', serif;
            margin: 0; padding: 40px;
            display: flex; justify-content: center;
        }

        .scrapbook {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
            gap: 40px;
            max-width: 1100px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        header { grid-column: 1 / -1; text-align: center; padding-bottom: 20px; }
        header h1 { font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive; font-size: 5rem; margin: 0; }

        /* Artists Grid - Hover Detail */
        .artist-gallery {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .polaroid {
            background: white;
            padding: 10px 10px 30px 10px;
            box-shadow: 3px 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            width: 150px;
            transition: 0.4s;
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .polaroid img { width: 100%; height: 150px; object-fit: cover; }
        .polaroid p { font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive; font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 10px; text-align: center; }

        .polaroid:hover { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(0deg); z-index: 10; }
        .polaroid-info {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            opacity: 0; transition: 0.3s; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.7rem;
        }
        .polaroid:hover .polaroid-info { opacity: 1; }

        /* Paper Scraps */
        .paper-scrap {
            background: #fdfaf0;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: relative;
        }
        .tape {
            position: absolute; width: 70px; height: 25px;
            background: var(--sage-tape);
            top: -12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-2deg);
        }

        /* About Me Section */
        .about-section { transform: rotate(-1deg); height: fit-content; }
        .about-section h3 { font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive; margin-top: 0; }

        /* Songs Section - Now with Hover Effect */
        .songs-section { transform: rotate(1deg); }
        .song-card {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px dotted #ccc; padding-bottom: 15px;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
            cursor: help;
        }
        .song-card img { 
            width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 4px; 
            box-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        
        .song-desc { 
            font-size: 0.8rem; 
            line-height: 1.4;
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
        }

        /* Hover trigger for Songs */
        .song-card:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); padding-left: 10px; border-radius: 10px; }
        .song-card:hover img { transform: scale(1.1); }
        .song-card:hover .song-desc {
            max-height: 100px;
            opacity: 1;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) { .scrapbook { display: block; } .artist-gallery { flex-wrap: wrap; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="scrapbook">
    <header>
        <h1>Gab</h1>
        <p>— A soul full of stories and dreams —</p>
    </header>

    <div class="artist-gallery">
        <div class="polaroid" style="transform: rotate(-3deg);">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/Clairo.jpg" alt="Clairo">
            <p>Clairo</p>
            <div class="polaroid-info">Bedroom pop that feels like a warm hug.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid" style="transform: rotate(2deg);">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/CocteuTwins.jpg" alt="Cocteau Twins">
            <p>Cocteau Twins</p>
            <div class="polaroid-info">The architects of ethereal dream pop.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid" style="transform: rotate(-1deg);">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/FleetwoodMac.jpg" alt="Fleetwood Mac">
            <p>Fleetwood Mac</p>
            <div class="polaroid-info">Legendary rock with perfect vocal harmonies.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid" style="transform: rotate(4deg);">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/WeyesBlood.jpg" alt="Weyes Blood">
            <p>Weyes Blood</p>
            <div class="polaroid-info">A modern take on 70s baroque pop.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid" style="transform: rotate(-2deg);">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/MattMaltese.jpg" alt="Matt Maltese">
            <p>Matt Maltese</p>
            <div class="polaroid-info">Dystopian romance and indie piano ballads.</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <article class="paper-scrap about-section">
        <div class="tape"></div>
        <h3>About Me</h3>
        <p>Hello! I'm <b>Gabriel<b>.</p>
        <p>A 20-year-old 2nd-year Nursing student at Bicol University Tabaco.</p>
        <p>I enjoy listening to music, binge-watching films, and sleeping.</p>
        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px dashed #ccc; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p style="font-style: italic; font-size: 0.85rem;">
            "Love isn't something that weak people do. Being a romantic takes a hell of a lot of hope." <br>
            <span style="font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive; display: block; margin-top: 5px;">— Fleabag</span>
        </p>
    </article>

    <article class="paper-scrap songs-section">
        <div class="tape"></div>
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive;">Favorite Songs</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; opacity: 0.6; margin-bottom: 15px;">(Hover to read more)</p>
        
        <div class="song-card">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/harbor.jpg" alt="Harbor">
            <div>
                <strong>Harbor — Clairo</strong>
                <div class="song-desc">
                    A quiet realization of a relationship’s end and the weight of being an emotional anchor.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="song-card">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/rilkeanheart.jpg" alt="Rilkean Heart">
            <div>
                <strong>Rilkean Heart — Cocteau Twins</strong>
                <div class="song-desc">
                    A poetic, shimmering dream about intense connection and tribute to Jeff Buckley.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="song-card">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/f8c01717babdbb0a51867d5b9086e5143328f682/images/Andromeda.jpg" alt="Andromeda">
            <div>
                <strong>Andromeda — Weyes Blood</strong>
                <div class="song-desc">
                    Exploring the struggle of opening your heart while feeling lost in the vast past.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="song-card">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/dreams.jpg" alt="Dreams">
            <div>
                <strong>Dreams — Fleetwood Mac</strong>
                <div class="song-desc">
                    A classic anthem about loneliness, freedom, and the cycle of love and loss.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="song-card">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/Ironywouldhaveit.jpg" alt="Irony">
            <div>
                <strong>As the Irony Would Have It — Matt Maltese</strong>
                <div class="song-desc">
                    A humorous yet emotional ballad about the unpredictable timing of romance.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</div>

</body>
</html>
